==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Untack
<hw>Un*tack"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>tack</ets>.]</ety> <def>To separate, as what is
tacked; to disjoin; to release.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>being <qex>untacked</qex> from honest cares.</q>
<rj><qau>Barrow.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Untackle</ent>⟦br⟧
